  ngtcp2: rework the return value handling of ngtcp2_conn_writev_stream
  
  Rework the return value handling of ngtcp2_conn_writev_stream and treat
  NGTCP2_ERR_STREAM_SHUT_WR separately.
  
  Closes #7546

